---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
--- 
<BaseLayout title="Relatório ESG">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="h-1 w-12 bg-primary rounded-full"></span>
            <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Relatório de Governança</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight leading-tight text-white">
            Transparência e <br/><span class="text-primary">Impacto Social</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Compromisso com a integridade e resultados reais. Acompanhe como transformamos investimentos em oportunidades para milhares de jovens.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <button class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/5 transition-colors text-white">
            <span class="material-icons text-primary text-sm">file_download</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Relatório Anual 2023 (PDF)</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Alunos Ativos</p>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary">1.542</span>
          <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold flex items-center"><span class="material-icons text-xs">trending_up</span> +12%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 w-full bg-primary/5 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-primary h-full w-[78%]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Empresas Parceiras</p>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary">48</span>
          <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold flex items-center"><span class="material-icons text-xs">trending_up</span> +5</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 w-full bg-primary/5 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-primary h-full w-[65%]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Horas de Formação</p>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary">12.8k</span>
          <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-bold">Total Acumulado</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 w-full bg-primary/5 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-primary h-full w-[90%]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Custo por Aluno/Ano</p>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary">R$ 4.2k</span>
          <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold flex items-center"><span class="material-icons text-xs">keyboard_arrow_down</span> -3%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 w-full bg-primary/5 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-primary h-full w-[45%]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-1 bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Alocação de Investimentos</h3>
        <div class="relative w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-10">
          <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full border-[18px] border-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="block text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary">R$ 2.4M</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Total 2023</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border-[18px] border-transparent border-t-primary border-r-primary rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-primary/5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Educação e Treinamento</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">45%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg border border-primary/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Infraestrutura</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">30%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg border border-primary/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-200"></span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Operações</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">25%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Crescimento do Impacto (2020 - 2023)</h3>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">Investimento</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">Alunos Formados</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-[300px] flex items-end justify-between gap-4 pt-4 border-b border-slate-800">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center gap-1 items-end h-full">
              <div class="w-6 chart-gradient-1 rounded-t h-[40%]"></div>
              <div class="w-6 bg-emerald-400/40 rounded-t h-[30%]"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 mt-2">2020</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center gap-1 items-end h-full">
              <div class="w-6 chart-gradient-1 rounded-t h-[55%]"></div>
              <div class="w-6 bg-emerald-400/50 rounded-t h-[45%]"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 mt-2">2021</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center gap-1 items-end h-full">
              <div class="w-6 chart-gradient-1 rounded-t h-[75%]"></div>
              <div class="w-6 bg-emerald-400/70 rounded-t h-[65%]"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 mt-2">2022</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center gap-1 items-end h-full">
              <div class="w-6 chart-gradient-1 rounded-t h-[95%]"></div>
              <div class="w-6 bg-emerald-400 rounded-t h-[88%]"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 mt-2 text-primary">2023</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Meta para 2024</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2.000 Alunos</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Expansão para 3 novas regiões</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Eficiência Operacional</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">+18%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Otimização de custos de sede</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Central de Relatórios</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Acesse nossos documentos oficiais e prestações de contas.</p>
        </div>
        <button class="text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:underline">Ver todo o histórico</button>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="group bg-slate-800/50 border border-primary/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-primary/40 transition-all">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuADAP2ar6NN9cOjU1p1pGU50yEjVfXlqqd7RDMR5zVOe4n-A6UEhWedPIqgB6UImsllJODc6-6DciB3RaeS9RPzaormyiRL3J_ngODhJdv7bkMCpNoHgtQl7zr8-odbrUuENHFi2d7qtZ0njBIJcIMR7bDWajY3w9qrModoSk9_-BBGpv67CYrry6AZiSi8a0JARBUZqy25YO6J-nxpN3uzCRbewOrkv5mvfzyjeGmi9hckneRX7Fh4SbMj-yBXFbtzJwd0mAtp1eo"/>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <span class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">DESTAQUE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Relatório Anual 2023</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">PDF • 12.4 MB</p>
              </div>
              <span class="material-icons text-primary bg-primary/5 p-2 rounded-lg">description</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6 line-clamp-2">
              Análise completa de resultados, demonstrações financeiras auditadas e histórias de sucesso.
            </p>
            <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm group-hover:bg-primary/80 transition-colors">
              <span class="material-icons text-sm">download</span>
              Baixar Agora
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-slate-800/50 border border-primary/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-primary/40 transition-all">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAGSk1V0RcI2JRyn-2jAW0lATBoolA8q45k4CyZYd2wEmxg5_KOcToEFuNp8bbwLfoQpFtvECYc5t6mritofiHB5LCTjeDRIlYIiJs0RMECHngy8lxWgn1h2HUyn05FNP6I-jm4ghhMJQtElUGo9d26CtHEOz8ey9IQOowj11THEc4_pcY4Oron6_s4NZDdn6Rpwnr9Mhf_2lCkNoHwGcZOyZ93MrYEAdiBmdOdx-MFTyuwgo5X6zJneSkBSPbnDvXvybd5dbVNqp4"/>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/60 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Impacto Socioeconômico</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">PDF • 8.1 MB</p>
              </div>
              <span class="material-icons text-primary bg-primary/5 p-2 rounded-lg">analytics</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6 line-clamp-2">
              Estudo sobre o retorno social do investimento e inserção no mercado de trabalho.
            </p>
            <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-slate-700 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm hover:bg-slate-700/50 transition-colors text-white">
              <span class="material-icons text-sm text-primary">download</span>
              Baixar Agora
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-slate-800/50 border border-primary/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-primary/40 transition-all">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAuJCWhs8U0j8HERwQRjJoaouf0GgkJnEiyvUKnWbco93YaD5EtPNAjMl7vu4nqgzWf70jcs8-z7QTPmDJepCX0V6R5gVwZj0SPfV-81wmPm7lZsopk793p_SpnIMHf6fTepbSAd1T2nhooMyPCBDRHeY_2h2zoQXf5WJA3MTjPj1p1rjA4F6kYvHsAuLXbSjDfIVnt0OozBiNvuztTeZn8MpWswNqXZ2606g2gGwfE8rhXolZ7UeUJrnVOm8SywVGvKZsqCDbWPEE"/>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/60 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1 text-white">Estatuto e Governança</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">PDF • 2.5 MB</p>
              </div>
              <span class="material-icons text-primary bg-primary/5 p-2 rounded-lg">gavel</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6 line-clamp-2">
              Nossas diretrizes éticas, regimento interno e estrutura de conselho administrativo.
            </p>
            <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-slate-700 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm hover:bg-slate-700/50 transition-colors text-white">
              <span class="material-icons text-sm text-primary">download</span>
              Baixar Agora
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-primary/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full border-4 border-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <span class="material-icons text-primary text-5xl">verified</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-extrabold text-xl text-white">Selo de Transparência</p>
          <p class="text-primary font-bold text-sm">AUDITADO 2023</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ética e Compliance como Base</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          O Projeto Novos Horizontes é submetido a auditorias externas anuais para garantir que cada centavo investido chegue ao seu destino final: o desenvolvimento do jovem. Nossas contas estão abertas para consulta pública e somos certificados pelas principais agências de fomento social.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-icons text-emerald-500 text-sm">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Auditoria Independente</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-icons text-emerald-500 text-sm">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">ISO 9001 Certificada</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-primary/10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-icons text-emerald-500 text-sm">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Conselho Ativo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>